    <p><strong>Hello</strong>, my name is Lucas Forde, I am a freelance web designer and developer based in Tunbridge Wells. I have over 20 years’ experience designing websites, building web applications, and maintaining online products for businesses across a range of industries. I offer my clients support with new websites and landing pages, changes and improvements to existing websites, and email marketing campaigns.</p>

    <p>Since I began my career, much of the web industry has become increasingly remote and impersonal. I believe there is still real value in working with someone local, easy to reach, and easy to communicate with. My fees are negotiable and agreed before work begins, with revisions expected and included in the quote. For smaller projects, I don’t ask for a deposit. If you decide the completed work isn’t right for your business, I won’t charge you for it.</p>

    <p>If your website needs updating, or you have a web project in mind, please get in touch.</p>
